geoffrey britton ( born 1 august 1943 , in lewisham , south east london ) is a rock drummer known for his work with paul mccartney & wings from august 1974 to january 1975 , where he was featured on the venus and mars album .

the 1970s music scene : in 1974 paul mccartney formed a new version of this group with drummer geoff britton & guitarist jimmy mcculloch

wings